sourcesContent: import React, { useState } from "react"; import "./styles.scss"; import { Box, Button, Hidden, Grid, List, ListItem, ImageList, ImageListItem, Fab, Typography, } from "@material-ui/core"; import SettingsIcon from "@material-ui/icons/Settings"; import HeaderNav from "./HeaderNav"; import SideBar from "./SideBar"; export default function Header() { const [toggleSide, setToggleSide] = useState(false); const onToggleSide = () => { setToggleSide(!toggleSide); }; return ( <> SIDEBAR FILTERS IMAGES ); }
